                "text": "The diagram shows the curve with equation \\(y=\\frac{1}{\\sqrt{x}} \\mathrm{e}^{\\sqrt{x}}\\) for \\(x \\geqslant 1\\), together with a set of \\(n-1\\) rectangles\nof unit width. of unit width.",
